<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
    <head>
    <% include!("common/header.stpl"); %>
    <meta name="keywords" content="Super Metroid, Map Randomizer, Map Rando, Map, Randomizer">
    <title>Super Metroid Map Rando</title>
    </head>
    <body>
    <% include!("common/navbar.stpl"); %>
    <div class="container col-xl-8 col-xxl-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center rounded-3 border shadow-lg m-4">
            <div class="col-lg-8 p-4">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Super Metroid Map Rando</h2>
                <p class="lead">After the planet Zebes exploded, Mother Brain put it back together again but arranged it differently.</p>
                <p class="lead">Can you find the items needed to defeat Mother Brain and restore peace to the galaxy?</p>
                <div class="text-center m-3">
                    <a href="/generate" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Generate Game</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 overflow-hidden text-center my-0">
                <img src="/static/hero-map.png" height=320 style="image-rendering: pixelated;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container col-xxl-10">
        <div class="row m-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Important tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Save frequently, to avoid losing progress in case of unexpected death.
                    <li>Don't go a way you can't come back from, except as a last resort.
                    <li>Before giving up, check the spoiler map to see what the game intended.
                    <li>There is a community happy to help if you need it. Find us on
                        <a href="https://discord.gg/Gc99YV2ZcB">Discord</a>!
                        This is a work in progress, so we appreciate feedback.
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Things to know</h3>
                <ul>
                <li>Even on its lowest difficulty settings, this is a challenging randomizer.
                <li>Expect to encounter dangerous enemies and softlock risks early on.
                <li>Rolling saves allow you to go back to an earlier save if you get stuck.
                <li>The game won't expect you to go down a one-way path for an item unless there is a way back
                    without using the item.
                <li>Many options are available to add variety and fit your style of play.
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</html>
